storyInfo: Xiaohei tries to find someone to care for Biu while they go on a mission. A few robots volunteer.

attributes.text: A Day in the Life of Biu

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Where are the ingredients?
attributes.name: Cafeteria Staff

attributes.content: The dishes?
attributes.name: Cafeteria Staff

attributes.content: Did someone let Kay in?
attributes.name: Cafeteria Staff

attributes.content: That thing keeps changing colors! How does it do that?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Where did they find this? It's just like me.
attributes.name: Ethan

attributes.content: Be nice to him, medical.
attributes.name: Ethan

attributes.content: Wait, you want to give me a check up too?
attributes.name: Ethan

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Where did that toy go?
attributes.name: Playing Child

attributes.content: Oh no, Instructor Dur-nar must've come to bring me back! What do I do?
attributes.name: Truant Child

attributes.content: No need to panic. Just say you came looking for the toy that mysteriously went missing, and accidentally stumbled on a secret in the depths of Rhodes Island...
attributes.name: Calm Child

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Chiave

attributes.content: No joke?
attributes.name: Chiave

attributes.content: I want in on this.
attributes.name: Chiave

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: What the heck are you? What are you doing?!
attributes.name: Engineering Operator

attributes.content: That's a machine component, you can't eat it!
attributes.name: Engineering Operator

attributes.content: Oh. Ms. Christine?
attributes.name: Engineering Operator

attributes.content: Whew, that's a relief. I should thank Phantom. He may look hard to get along with, but he's got a heart of gold.
attributes.name: Engineering Operator

attributes.content: Have a nice day, madam!
attributes.name: Engineering Operator

attributes.content: Biu...!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Gotcha!
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: Why won't you listen, Biu?
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: You'll get hurt if you keep running around like this!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: What's with this color?
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Looks like he ate a lot.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: So where did you find him, Xiaohei?
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: The room at the end of the hallway.
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: He also went to the toyhouse and the restaurant, and ate some of the food and toys. Without permission.
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: Whoops... Guess we'll have to apologize.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Yes, and keep a close eye on him.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Okay. Let's go!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: So Biu didn't cause too much damage, and even caught an operator who skipped class?
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: And that fierce-looking red guy over there... was talking about digging something up, and now he's leaving by himself... Oh, he's looking this way!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: I'm sorry, Instructor Dur-nar! I won't do it again!
attributes.name: Truant Child

attributes.content: Don't worry, brother, I'll complete the mission!
attributes.name: Chiave

attributes.content: ...How touching.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Nice job, Biu.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: So, apparently we won't need to pay any compensation, just do a few missions for them.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Does that mean Biu can't come with us?
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Yeah, but they gave us a cage to put him in.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: But we still need to find someone to take care of him...
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Mmph! Ohhhh!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: The ingenious Master Closure has added so many features with this update!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I can feel my passion break through and shine even brighter!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Our storage capacity has increased by 35.7%, allowing us to download and install more engineering-related files.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I've been updated with more first aid procedures and language modules, further enhancing my support capabilities.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I especially appreciate the ability to recover deleted files. I recovered a recording of the Doctor snoring from a few years ago. Would you like to hear it?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Wow!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: What are those?
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: Robots? Talking to each other?
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Good morning, unfamiliar lady and gentlemen! Are you in awe of my perfect form?
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I knew no one could resist my scorching charisma!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Unknown personnel detected. Do you require assistance from Rhodes Island?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I can help you if you're not feeling well.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Wow, they really can talk!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Hi there, we're new here, but we have a pet who needs to be looked after while we're away. Do you know anyone who can help us?
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: A pet?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Not a problem! This update includes 956 volumes on pet care, encompassing every species of plant and animal known to be kept for recreational purposes. I guarantee my burning core will keep them warm!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I can also help when they are not feeling well.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I have extensive experience in caring for operators.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Really? Wow, amazing!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: More than amazing, incredible! For I, Closure's masterpiece, will singlehandedly solve all your problems!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: (Whisper) Are they spirits?
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: Smart robots, Xiaohei. Way more advanced than the ones we're used to, though. They may not look like people, but they definitely talk like people.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: The technology here is incredible.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: So, he says he knows a lot about caring for pets. I think we can trust him. What about you guys?
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Hm... Why not?
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: It wouldn't be easy to find someone else on short notice... Alright then.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Stay here, Heixiu.
attributes.name: Xiaohei

attributes.content: Hey-xiu!
attributes.name: Heixiu

attributes.content: Oooh! What an adorable black blob! Sitting right on my outer frame!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Haha. We'll leave things to you then!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: And don't give Biu any metal or living things. It's dangerous!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: You can take him out of the cage if Heixiu's around.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: But he's still very excited, so keep him locked up for a little longer.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Understood. Please register your names and that of your pets, to be uploaded to the terminal as a mission.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Thanks!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Biu! Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Behavior analysis indicates a desire to go out and play.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Let him ride on my broad back! I'll show him every corner of Rhodes Island!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Biu?
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: He's clawing at the cage. Is he not feeling well?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Hey, why does he not talk?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Querying the latest language modules.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I seem to have previously deleted some language data. Allow me to restore it...
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Eat my shorts, berk, guan ni pi shi...!
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Analysis indicates this is from a collection of Terran expletives that was accidentally added to your library. The engineering department prepared a plugin for you because of this.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Apologies... I have re-deleted them.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: No, no, time waits for no man. I can't hold back my core's burning passion anymore! Put the cage on my back, and let's depart!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Hold on. According to '100 Tips on Keeping a Pet,' animals demonstrate stress reactions when exposed to an unfamiliar environment.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: This is because they are unsure if it is safe or not. We must create an environment for Biu that is absolutely safe.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Acknowledged! Scouting the nearby environment.
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Scouting! Scouting!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Failed! Feature not found!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I will do it.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Hallway confirmed safe.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: There is no need to worry, Biu.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Is he trembling?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: It may be a stress reaction.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu! (I wanna go out and play!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: What do we do?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Let me give him a check-up.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu! (I wanna go out and play!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Data within expected range. We can go.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Ooorah! Let's go!!!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Do you want to go out and play?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: We cannot. The operators said he is still excited, and that it will be dangerous.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I must scan each room to ensure absolute safety.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Chirp...
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Don't be frustrated, little one! I'll give you the full tour during the long wait!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: This is the Rhodes Island rest area. Operators put up stalls over there from time to time, where you can buy whatever you like!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I doubt Biu would be interested in shopping.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Chirp...
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Then what about the workshop? I can't wait to bring him inside!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Biu! Biu! (I wanna go!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Scan complete. The garage contains large quantities of metal, indicating a high degree of danger.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Chirp...
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Continuing scan of conveyor area.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Hey, what's that?
attributes.name: Operator Passerby

attributes.content: Gummy said he's a big eater! Want some fries?
attributes.name: Curious Operator

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Oh, he's so cute!
attributes.name: Curious Operator

attributes.content: Come on, eat up, I have more where that came from!
attributes.name: Operator Passerby

attributes.content: Apologies, operators, but his owner warned us not to feed him because it's dangerous.
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I see.
attributes.name: Operator Passerby

attributes.content: Sorry.
attributes.name: Curious Operator

attributes.content: So what about the conveyor area? I can't stop myself from overheating anymore!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Biu! Biu! (I wanna go!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Scan complete. The conveyor area contains conveyor belts, indicating a high degree of danger.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu...
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Scan complete. A high degree of danger.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu...
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Scan complete. A high degree of danger.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu, you need to stay within a 5-meter area in this hallway. Both ahead and behind are too dangerous.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: You must remain in this cage until you calm down, to ensure your own safety.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu...
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Biu is looking even worse. Is he afraid of the outside?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu! Biu! (No! No!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: He became more excited upon hearing your words. I gather you were correct.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Let's return. Scans indicate a large amount of metal and living beings in these rooms, but no wood, making it dangerous.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Here is some disinfected wood. According to 'Pets for Dummies,' it is ideal to feed once every 2.5 hours.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Here, an appropriate portion.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu! Biu! (It's too little!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: The serving size has been meticulously calculated. The next feeding will occur in 2.5 hours.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: According to 'How to Make Your Pet Love You,' one must always be attentive to their physical and mental state.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: One hour has elapsed since the last check-up. I must perform another check-up to ensure that you are healthy, and continue to do so every hour.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu!!! (I'm gonna bite your head off!)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Biu... (No, Xiaobai said not to...)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Biu... (Sob...)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Come on, Biu, turn on your back and let me check your pulse...
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.text: Biu and the Terrible, Horrible, No Good, Very Bad Day

attributes.content: I observed the black blob open Biu's cage, causing Biu to flee into a corner of the hallway.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I am unable to bend down, so I do not know where he went.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: But I can hear him run away as soon as we approach.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: He seems to be avoiding us.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I'm sorry, Biu! Were you scorched by my burning passion?!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I haven't learned to cool it down, but I'll control myself for your sake if you don't like it!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: For that is my duty!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Biu remains stationary beneath a box.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Heixiu is still here, which means Biu is safe, but keeping his distance.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I ran another self-diagnostic. There is no error with my programming. Every step was taken in accordance with the instruction in the books.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I do not understand why this is happening.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Perhaps we should ask other operators for assistance.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: But we clearly did exactly as instructed, and have not had similar issues when interacting with operators...
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: What could be the issue?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu? Biu? Where are you?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: I just reported back, Lancet-2. I heard Biu is with you, but I don't see him.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Hello, Operator Rockrock!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: While I would love to share the burning warmth of my core with you, we need your help!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: We have a situation here, Operator Rockrock.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Based on your interactions, how did Ah Gen and the others take care of Biu?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: We followed the pet care manuals to the letter, but ran into some trouble.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Hmm... let me think...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Uh oh, Biu, what did you just eat?
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: He's turned black, with red and white dots on him.
attributes.name: Ah Gen

attributes.content: Eek!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Er, I think he just ate the comb I made.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Oh, I'm so sorry!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: It's fine, there's plenty of wood for me to make another one.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: But does he eat wood?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Yup! Biu loves wood. He even made a big hole in my grandpa's house!
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: ...And you're that happy about that?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Teehee.
attributes.name: Xiaobai

attributes.content: Fine, just give him what he wants.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: He ended up eating most of the materials I brought. And I was planning on making something, too. Oh well.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: There you are.
attributes.name: Rockrock
Rockrock
attributes.content: Let me rub your tummyâ€”

attributes.name: Rockrock
attributes.content: You're starving, aren't you?
Here, my last two pieces of wood...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: But it's not feeding timeâ€”
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Your machine has not yet been scannedâ€”
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: It must be disinfected firstâ€”
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: (Swallow)
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Well, now he's a light yellow. Looks like the wood wasn't thoroughly dried. Thanks, Biu.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Oh, there you are, Heixiu.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: There was no scan, nor is it feeding time. Your actions are not in accordance with the manuals.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: But Biu came out of his own accord, and he looks happy.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Thank you, Operator Rockrock! You have relit my core, which had gone cold at not being able to solve the problem!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Yeah, so just do it like that.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Let him run around and eat whatever he wants. Other people can hold him too, as long as Heixiu's around.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Don't overthink it.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: We should relax our parameters? I can try.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: ...Biu, I have a piece of wood here. Would you like it?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Chirp!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: You are feeding him directly?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Yeah. Look at how flat his tummy is. He's hungry. Just give him something to eat and he'll take a nap.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: What about the unfamiliar environment?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Heixiu's around, so no worries.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Can others feed him too?
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Sure, as long as it's not metallic or alive.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Understood. Thank you, Operator Rockrock.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Alright, I gotta get going.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Have a nice day.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Lancet-2, I think we can delete some of the books in our library.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Or all of them.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu has responded better to Rockrock's methods than the ones we have recorded.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: You're absolutely right! We must warm Biu with our burning cores!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: I will retain 'Basic Pet Habits,' to ensure that I have essential veterinary knowledge.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I was originally designed to care for operators, after all.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Is that ok, Biu?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Where do you want to go, then?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Wherever you like!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: My warmth will always be by your side!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: We can just follow him.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Wooow, look at that setting sun!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: It's lit a fire in my core!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: And look how stylishly Biu eats, like the wind sweeping through the clouds!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Did you install a module of Yanese expressions, THRM-EX?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: The amazing Doctor did! They believed it would help me convey my thoughts even better!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: And it just happens to have an expression that describes Biu perfectly!
attributes.name: THRM-EX
THRM-EX
attributes.content: Round and plump!
Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: According to Ah Gen, they should be about done with their mission soon.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: No wonder Biu wanted to get out.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Did you like the food from the cafeteria, Biu?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: That said, the staff were a little sad to see you ignore their dishes and go straight for the chopsticks.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Fortunately, operators from Yan or Higashi are rare, so we have plenty to spare.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Look, Biu likes it!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Oooooohhh!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Oooooohhh!!!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: He's approaching me for the very first time! He likes me! I can't control the heat of my coreâ€”
attributes.name: THRM-EX
THRM-EX
attributes.content: Oh, I'm burning... burning!
Good thing I have the cold spray first-aid module. That seemed effective on you.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: If only Biu could install language modules.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: My programming has determined that that would be illegal.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I mean, if only he could communicate with us.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Taking care of a creature that cannot speak is much more difficult than expected.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: At least we didn't fail the mission.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Thank you, Biu. I am not equipped with an emotion chip, but my core is instructing me to sing a folk song for you. Would you like me to play it?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: It feels as though my clock speed is dropping. Why is that?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Oh, it's back to normal.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu! Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: Ride on me and we'll climb the hill ahead of us. That way, we can see the vehicles headed back to the ship.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Would you like to ride on me, or walk by yourself?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: You want to go by yourself?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu darts through branches, bushes, and rocks towards the peak of the hill.
The setting sun shines on him and the robots.
Lancet-2, THRM-EX, can you sing?
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: I looked up a song that I previously learned.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: 'â™ªMy parents want me to be a lawyerâ™ª'
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: 'â™ªMy grandparents want me to form a familyâ™ª'
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: 'â™ªBut all I want to do is pick up my brushâ™ª'
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: 'â™ªAnd draw this sunsetâ™ª'
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Can Biu draw the sunset, Castle-3?
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: I am unable to answer this question.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: But the way he runs around under the setting sun shows that he is happy.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Biu! Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: It is what he likes to do.
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: â™ªThat is all good, but I love the sunset the mostâ™ª'
attributes.name: Castle-3

attributes.content: Hey, I can see the sunset reflecting off the vehicles on their way back!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Let's go meet them with my burning passion!
attributes.name: THRM-EX

attributes.content: Please wait while I update my database.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Update complete. Let us go.
attributes.name: Lancet-2

attributes.content: Biu!
attributes.name: Biu

attributes.content: The robots follow behind Biu, leaving long clouds of dust in their wake.
A line of text flashes across Closure's robot monitoring terminal.
'Worry not and enjoy the present.'
